Package at.tuwien.ifs.somtoolbox.apps.viewer3d Description

This package implements the 3-dimensional version of the SOMViewer application. The stand-alone version can be started using the SOMViewer3D class. Moreover, the 3D viewer can be opened from within the SOMViewer.
